item.title: About
item.description: I opened this site entirely for the sake of creating a second brain, observing my development process and improving myself. Maybe I will note what I have learned here, maybe not, I don’t know. My only goal is to observe the development process of myself. I don’t need someone to read it, but if someone reads this article, welcome to my schizophrenia world.
